Originally focused on neurotrophic factors and their regenerative capabilities, giving rise to its name, the company then branched out into the study of both cytokine and tyrosine kinase receptors.
Address: 777 OLD SAW MILL RIVER ROAD, TARRYTOWN, NY, US
